    var storedName = localStorage.getItem("user");
    if (storedName) {
        window.location.href = "home.html"; // Redirect to home.html if user is already logged in
    }
};

document.getElementById("name").addEventListener("keypress", function(event) {
    if (event.key === "Enter") {
        username(); // Call the username function when Enter is pressed
    }
});
</script>
</html>
```

### Explanation:
- **Check on Page Load**: The `window.onload` function checks if there is a `user` stored in `localStorage`. If a user is found, it automatically redirects to `home.html`.
- **Storage and Redirection**: When a user enters their name and presses "Enter" or clicks the button, their name is stored in `localStorage`, and they are redirected to `home.html`."}],"context":{"currentFile":{"path":"index.html","fsPath":"/Users/Sakshi/PycharmProjects/fintrack/index.html","sources":["opened_tab"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>
