### JavaScript

Add an event listener for the edit button to handle the edit profile functionality:

```javascript
document.getElementById("editButton").addEventListener("click", function() {
  // Redirect to an edit profile page or open a modal for editing
  window.location.href = "editProfile.html"; // Assuming you have an editProfile.html page
});
```

