- The `.button` class styles the button with a background color of `#03c6fc`, white text, padding, and rounded corners.
- The `width: 70%;` and `margin: 20px auto;` properties ensure the button is the same width as the input field and centered within the parent container. Adjust the `padding`, `font-size`, and other properties as needed to fit your design preferences."}],"context":{"currentFile":{"path":"index.html","fsPath":"/Users/Sakshi/PycharmProjects/fintrack/index.html","sources":["opened_tab"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>
